# The public espalier repository is an artifact repository.
# Ignore everything by default, then admit only generated release artifacts and
# safe repository scaffold files.

*

!.gitignore
!README.md
!RELEASE_ARTIFACTS.md
!package.json
!LICENSE
!CHANGELOG.md
!custom-elements.json
!espalier.css-data.json
!espalier.token-manifest.json

!dist/
!dist/**

!css/
!css/**

!license/
!license/**
